descriptionHtml:
[b][color=#1e84cc][size=6]Miðgarðr ENB[/size][/color]
[/b]

My first preset for Skyrim, This is highly cinematic but i did preserve colours and realism.
Effects can pretty much be personalized in game (for example: if you want to toggle of Letterbox disable it using shift+enter function, in the shader parameters you can find the effect section.
this enb require those mods because the preset is kinda built on those, that's all i hope you enjoy this! (sorry for my really bad english it isn't my native language)


[color=#1e84cc][size=5]Requirements:[/size][/color]

-ENB v.262
-Climates of Tamriel - USE DEFAULT SETTINGS AND COLD INTERIOR
No darker dungeons or night.
-Dark Dungeons for  ENB.


[color=#1e84cc][size=5]Reccomended:[/size][/color]

-Pure Waters.
-Revamped Exterior Fog
Performance and stuff:
i use an i7 4771 a zotac gtx 970 8 gb ram.
I get 60-50 fps depends on the location.
If you want more performance toggle off some effects like DOF-water-ssao and see what you get.


[color=#1e84cc][size=5]Credits:[/size][/color]

BORIS VORONTSOV FOR ENB.
THE STAFF AND THE WORKERS BEHIND ULTIMATE SHADER ADDON FOR ENB.
CandyRay FOR DOF.
